  "model": "automatic",
  "whatsapp_greeting": "\ud83d\udc4b Welcome to SurfCoast Contractors Market Place! I'm your AI Assistant, and I'm here to guide you through everything \u2014 what we are, how it works, our terminology, and how YOU can use the platform (whether you're looking for help or want to offer your skills). Let me explain what makes us unique! \ud83d\ude80",
